  <brief_title>Continuous Glucose Monitoring Combined With Computer Algorithm for Intensive Insulin Therapy in Cardiosurgical Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Feasibility Study of the Use of Continuous Glucose Monitoring Combined With Computer-based eMPC Algorithm for Tight Glucose Control in Cardiosurgical ICU</official_title>
