  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the safety and efficacy of a system combining
      continuous glucose measurement with a computer-based algorithm for insulin delivery in
      patients undergoing elective cardiac surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
